data.description:
A Wonderful Classic American Model Home, the Ohio plan. The open floor plan display's the beautiful kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and rich cabinets with crown molding. It's open to a large living and dining area. Four spacious bedrooms with two baths. Master bedroom zoned separate with large walk in closet, bath with separate shower and garden tub. Pretty interior colors. 
Please visit Model home located at 7876 Enchanted Park Dr., El Paso, TX 79911 Open Daily 10AM-5:30PM
 Photos for demonstration purposes only not of actual home.
